    • Method Detail

      • loadProps

        public ConfigBuilder loadProps(Properties props,
                               String scopePrefix)
        Loads properties which have a given name prefix into the config. The following restrictions apply:
        • No property can have a name that is equal to the prefix
        • After removal of the prefix, the remaining property name should start with a letter.
        Parameters:
        props - the collection from where to load the properties
        scopePrefix - only properties with this prefix will be considered. The prefix will be removed from the names of the keys added to the Config object. The prefix can be an empty string but cannot be null.
